<h2>Add a new Park Pass</h2>
<p>To add a new park pass, please enter their information below and click `Submit`!</p>
<form id="add-parkPass-form" method="POST" action="/add-parkPass-form">

    <label for="input-parkPass">Park Pass Name: </label>
    <input type="text" name="input-parkPass" id="input-parkPass">

    <input type="submit">
</form>